reviewText: One of the first Jorge Negrete. I remember seeing it when I was 8 years old and forgot all about it. Well, it brought back memories and now I know why I forgot all about it. It is not the Jorge of his later pictures. Not even one song. I guess in the olden days it was ok to be burned at the stake in the public square. I bought it for my collection and that is what it's going to be, a collection item.
